404|        "PHASE_1_SCOUT\n\nFind all call sites for `{method_name}` across the repository.\n\n\
405|         Use ripgrep to locate candidate files, then ast_calls for function/method calls and \
406|         ast_constructions for struct/type construction literals. read_file small slices when needed. \
407|         Finish with a finalize report listing each file_path and line numbers or ranges in a machine-readable block:\n\
408|         ```refactor_targets\n[{{\"file_path\":\"...\",\"lines\":[...]}}]\n```\n\
409|         or for multi-line struct literals:\n\
410|         ```refactor_targets\n[{{\"file_path\":\"...\",\"ranges\":[{{\"start\":25,\"end\":32}}]}}]\n```"
411|    )
